transcript:

Customer: Hello sir, maine aapke jo mail hai na usme wo receipt to dal diya hai uska. 
Executive: Ji aap check kar le. Sir main ye ticket close kar du sir?
Customer: Haan bilkul.
Executive: Hello? Sir lekin main puchna lekin main ye puchna chah raha tha sir aap services pe sir kafi din se active nahi hai sir to kya reason hai sir iska?
Customer: Are bhai chhod de yaar mere bahut kam hai jab hum honge dekhenge usko. Tumhara payment ja raha hai tumhara kam chal gaya bas.
Executive: Ji.
Customer: Jo loss hai mera loss hai.
Executive: Ji.
Executive: Theek hai sir.
